00:08:00.150 --> 00:08:01.460
And I said yes.

00:08:01.460 --> 00:08:03.230
So he said, fair enough.

00:08:03.230 --> 00:08:05.570
And then he started teaching me.

00:08:05.570 --> 00:08:09.770
I think that made me
even more determined

00:08:09.770 --> 00:08:13.510
