we call Ustad poets,

00:08:21.990 --> 00:08:28.770
poets like [INAUDIBLE],,
and all those stalwarts.

00:08:28.770 --> 00:08:32.490
So I think that
really sort of got me

00:08:32.490 --> 00:08:37.990
into this entire
ghazal singing form.

00:08:37.990 --> 00:08:46.020
And I think this ultimately, I
guess, once I got in the world,

00:08:46.020 --> 00:08:48.562
