the first choice.

00:12:19.820 --> 00:12:21.860
The first choice
was always ghazals,

00:12:21.860 --> 00:12:25.270
and even today, it's ghazals.

00:12:25.270 --> 00:12:31.240
And then got to the stage
event, this particular film

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:32.140
